							<p>Visualise your voice</p>
						</span>
						<span>
							<p>Visualise your voice</p>
						</span>
						<span>
							<p>Visualise your voice</p>
						</span>
						<span>
							<p>Visualise your voice</p>
						</span>
					</div>
				</div>

			</div>

			<section id="requirements" class="container__participate">
				<div>
					<h3 class="year-season__text">{{entry.year}}&#124;{{entry.season}}<h3>
							<h2>Can I participate?</h2>
							<p>If you're between the<span class="bold">
									age of 16-25
								</span>
								and like to work in a group, then yes&#33; Every semester 30 people get chosen to participate in the workshops making films for the festival. Simply sign up in the form below and you will be notified about acceptance within 21 days</p>
							<a href="/{{('apply')}}" class="btn">I want to participate</a>
						</div>
						<img src="/public/can-i-image.png" alt="group picture happy people">
					</section>
				</div>
			</div>

			<section class="container__theme theme--bleed">
				<div class="container__theme--wrapper">
					<div>
						<h3>This years theme</h3>
						<h1>{{entry.titleTheme}}</h1>
					</div>
					<div class="theme__card">
						<h2>{{entry.paragraph}}</h2>
						<p>{{entry.subtitle}}</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="banner-theme">
					<div class="banner-theme-text">
						<span>
							<p>The future of Kortrijk</p>
						</span>
